msgstr "Python 行为的更改"

#: ../../whatsnew/3.7.rst:2224
msgid ""
":keyword:`async` and :keyword:`await` names are now reserved keywords. Code "
"using these names as identifiers will now raise a :exc:`SyntaxError`. "
"(Contributed by Jelle Zijlstra in :issue:`30406`.)"
